id: pm-g3xl
title: Drift-lock the .agents/plugins/marketplace.json (pm-local) manifest in the plugin contract test
description: "The repo has three marketplace manifests; the drift test reconciles only root marketplace.json and .claude-plugin/marketplace.json. The third, .agents/plugins/marketplace.json (name pm-local), has no test/code/docs reference and can silently rot (it currently lists only pm-codex and omits pm-claude, with no enforced version)."
